Mónica_Cruz http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mónica_Cruz 0 Mónica Cruz Sánchez (born 16 March 1977) is a Spanish actress, dancer and fashion designer. She is the younger sister of actress Penélope Cruz. She has appeared in films The Inquiry (2006), Last Hour (2008), Jerry Cotton (2010) and Iron Cross (2011). Mónica Cruz Sánchez (born 16 March 1977) is a Spanish actress, dancer and fashion designer. She is the younger sister of actress Penélope Cruz. She has appeared in films The Inquiry (2006), Last Hour (2008), Jerry Cotton (2010) and Iron Cross (2011).
